# {{musici}} a [[Japanese]] musical [[instrument]] having numerous [[string]]s, usually seven or thirteen, that are stretched over a [[convex]] wooden sounding board and are [[pluck]]ed with three [[plectra]], worn on the [[thumb]], [[index finger]], and [[middle finger]] of one hand.

